{
  "id": "adv_group_mna_01_12",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 01 12",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 4.833333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "あっここだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ I’m here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.133333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1933.3333333333362,
          "startTime": 7.06666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 7.066666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈、大丈夫か！？\nさっきの電話は一体……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana‚ are you okay?!\nWhat on earth was that call just now…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "実は、電車で居眠りしちゃって……\n気が付いたら東京まで行っちゃったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I ended up falling asleep on the train…\nWhen I woke up‚ I’d gone all the way to Tokyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 17.666666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "え……\nあんなに俺に注意しておいて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…?\nWeren’t you the one giving me all those warnings?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 21.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "お説教は後！\nタクシー代、足りなくなっちゃったの！　助けて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Save the lecture for later!\nAnd help me out. I don’t have enough money for the taxi fare!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そういう意味だったのか……\n心配したんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s what you meant…\nI was worried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6499.999999999996,
          "startTime": 36.03333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 31.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁはぁ、ごめんなさい\nお待たせしました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff huff‚ sorry.\nSorry to keep you waiting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "すぐにリハーサルに入るぞ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have to go straight to rehearsal!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……\n今日は迷惑かけてごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ummm…\nI’m sorry for causing you trouble today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "済んだことはもういいんだ\nそれよりこれからの話をしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry about it. It’s already over now.\nI’d rather talk about the future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、うん、これからは\n絶対にこんなミスしないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ okay. From now on‚\nI won’t mess up like this ever again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いや、今のままではきっと\nまた同じことが起こる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. If things stay as they are‚\nthe same thing will happen again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "え？　そんなことないよ\n{user}くんもマネージャーに復帰したし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? No‚ it won’t.\n{user} is back as my manager though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺がいるとかいないとか、そんなことは原因じゃない\n麻奈にも分かってるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not about whether I’m here or not.\nYou know that as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり仕事を減らそう\n今のスケジュールがそもそも過密過ぎるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s reduce your workload after all.\nYour schedule is too full right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "もし麻奈が体を壊したらどうなる？\nファンだって、三枝さんや遙子さんだって悲しむ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What will happen if you get sick?\nYou’ll disappoint your fans‚ Saegusa-san and Haruko-san as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-mna009.m4a",
      "text": "私は歌ってない方が、体の調子が悪くなるの！\n理屈じゃないの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m more likely to get sick if I’m not singing!\nIt’s not about what’s logical!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-mna010.m4a",
      "text": "絶対に迷惑かけないようにするから、お願い\n……私から歌を奪わないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t cause any more problems‚\n…So please don’t take singing away from me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（……こんな風に意見が対立するとは思いもしなかった）\n（どうするのが正しいんだ？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I never thought our opinions would conflict like this.）\n（What is the right thing to do?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈を最大限に輝かせるには……）\n（今の俺のやり方ではダメなんだろうか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Is the way I’m doing things now）\n（not enough to make Mana shine to her full potential…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-mna011.m4a",
      "text": "そんな顔しないで\nごめんね、わがまま言って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t make that face.\nI’m sorry for being selfish…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12/sud_vo_adv_group_mna_01_12-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "いや……俺こそごめん\n……事務所に帰ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. I’m the one who’s sorry.\nLet’s go back to the office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.36666666666667
    },
    {
